{"tid":1537831,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到入機場巴士站之後點算好","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:48:27.000Z","uid":227788,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9583fc2e6210ddccf76ab47d89e2f5297a18f18a","tid":1537831,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"-坐車入機場, 係捉精靈。<br />\n-如果有狗趕就巴士站等巴士(如果停哂都係企係度等, 唔好一見到防暴就跑, 跑走仲危險) <br />\n-不停咁loop.出到去又坐返去捉精靈<br />\n-記住零裝備, 乜都唔好帶, 旅客look, 唔好全黑。<br />\n<br />\n問題來了: 狗可能會亂捉人!!<br />\n對策: 任佢地拉, 你只係捉精靈同等巴士走。 無犯法。 捉左告唔入, 但可能比狗打一身。(會唔會因為怕比狗打唔出?)"},{"pid":"848aa92e345ed62fee374dfc137822c8d5c20558","tid":1537831,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d6d7d91b5135f334c886a4e4f6852fe931cb22d","tid":1537831,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"冇錯 唔好跑 繼續排隊禁手機<br />\n身上唔好帶任何有位入既野"},{"pid":"a08d47251dce36bccc038add790aeb0502ff6635","tid":1537831,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6d7d91b5135f334c886a4e4f6852fe931cb22d","tid":1537831,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"冇錯 唔好跑 繼續排隊禁手機<br />\n身上唔好帶任何有位入既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"如果跑離機場範圍仲危險。<br />\n啲狗做乜都得!"},{"pid":"28862264258d315615c21a6676d8fc37492237ee","tid":1537831,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9613bf53efb7bf29ca2cdd164256c26d82c7052","tid":1537831,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n記得帶身份證喺身"},{"pid":"53ecebb8c399303e8da99d84d266a2fdd9b4e8cd","tid":1537831,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"on撚鳩 你有冇裝都係又打又拉 仲叫人唔好帶係咪傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a5923b7701deeb2e82e6699f07092449c795c0","tid":1537831,"uid":261711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"要用咩理由入機場啊 有實q check登機證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5707a518eafb20c1f228b70384501be6a979f2","tid":1537831,"uid":5918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53ecebb8c399303e8da99d84d266a2fdd9b4e8cd","tid":1537831,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"on撚鳩 你有冇裝都係又打又拉 仲叫人唔好帶係咪傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:37: